    color: contextColor,
    size: contextSize,
    weight: contextWeight,
    mirrored: contextMirrored,
    ...restContext
  } = useContext(IconContext);

  return (
    <svg
      ref={ref}
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width={size ?? contextSize}

      fill={color ?? contextColor}

      transform={mirrored || contextMirrored ? "scale(-1, 1)" : undefined}

});
